Calculate the index of refraction for a medium in which the speed of light is <m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mtext>.</m:mtext><m:mtext>012</m:mtext><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:msup><m:mtext>10</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.25em"/><m:mtext> m/s</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>, and identify the most likely substance based on <link target-id="eip-69"/>.
